1. *Čisti* pod je veoma bitan za zdravlje. (Clean floor is very important for health.)
2. Moramo *očistiti* kuću pre nego što dođu gosti. (We need to clean the house before the guests arrive.)
3. On *čisti* automobil svake subote. (He cleans the car every Saturday.)
4. Koliko često ti *čistiš* svoju sobu? (How often do you clean your room?)
5. Molim vas da *očistite* svoje stolove pre nego što odete. (Please clean your desks before you leave.)
6. Mama *čisti* sudove dok tata čita novine. (Mom cleans the dishes while dad reads the newspaper.)
7. Moramo *očistiti* reke i jezera od zagađenja. (We need to clean the rivers and lakes from pollution.)
8. *Čisteći* kupatilo, pronašla sam novčić ispod ormarića. (While cleaning the bathroom, I found a coin under the cabinet.)
9. Danas sam *očistio* svoju radnu sobu i osećam se mnogo bolje. (Today I cleaned my workspace and I feel much better.)
10. *Čišćenje* snega sa ulice može biti veoma naporno. (Removing snow from the street can be very exhausting.)